Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:04.10,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A Grande Era dos Piratas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:09.23,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...está passando por uma onda que supera as expectativas do Governo Mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:18.07,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}E quem está no olho do \Nfuracão dessa onda imparável é...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.78,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:25.08,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}E os Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:31.33,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Para combater a turbulenta \NGrande Era dos Piratas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:36.42,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}cinquenta reis se reúnem a cada \Nquatro anos para uma assembleia mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.88,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}O Reverie está prestes a começar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:48.52,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Os tempos estão mudando\N a passos largos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.68,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,810)}{\fad(500,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,545)\fad(527,0)}NOVO MUNDO - NO MAR {one pace only infobox, check}
