Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.68,0:05:14.46,Title-207+,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&HE6E6E6&\blur0.8\fad(725,480)\pos(960,716.8)}O Quinto Yonkou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:58.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estou com fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:03.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:07.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Como você conseguiu isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:07.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:09.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estava no meu bolso.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:10.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:11.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É de verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:13.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:18.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\fad(0,519)}Você esqueceu que a Germa usa isso\N para se transformar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, aquela vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vou me transformar agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu primeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.31,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:29.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vou me livrar disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.98,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nem pense em jogar isso fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:35.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Se você fizer isso, eu vou procurar\N até no fundo do mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:37.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você não pode fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:38.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você não sabe nadar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:42.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estava no meu bolso, então\Nse for jogar fora, é melhor me dar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não, me dá aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:44.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:45.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:51.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Mas por que estava no bolso do Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Deve ter sido o Niji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:56.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\fad(0,393)}Com certeza foi para me irritar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:03.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não quero ficar mais forte\N usando esse lixo científico!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não seja precipitado, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}A ciência é uma fonte\N de poder incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por que vocês querem tanto isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:13.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Se eu usar o Raid Suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:13.06,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}Se eu usar o Raid Suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}talvez possamos soltar raios!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.99,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}talvez possamos soltar raios!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que bobagem, vocês são crianças?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:26.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Com o Franky já temos membros\N o suficiente com acessórios!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:27.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu quero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:31.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você insultou a ciência?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.12,Sanji in Love,,0,0,0,,{}Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:36.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Claro que não insultei a ciência!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:39.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Meu Sorcery Clima Tact foi criado\N com a ciência do clima...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:42.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...e as habilidades do Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É incrível estar dentro do Tact!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você realmente a seguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não acredito que preferiu comida\N à lealdade à Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Consegui um servo poderoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}N-Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Zeus, não se esqueça.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu sou servo da Nami-san\N há muito mais tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:13.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Mas eu vivo dentro do Tact que\N a Nami carrega o tempo todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você está brigando com vapor d'água...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Lá vou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Em marcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por que não funciona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.92,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}Por que não funciona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:24.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não chorem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Com certeza só você pode ativar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Faça isso, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não sou da Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Escutem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Germa 66!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vinsmoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não digam essas palavras na minha frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Transforme-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.90,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}Transforme-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E-Ei, me soltem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Chegou o jornal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Tem alguma informação sobre nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Uma foto do Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Tem algo sobre o Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não diz o que aconteceu depois?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:02.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, Jinbe, Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Parece que não fala nada sobre isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:09.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Só diz que Luffy, Sanji, Jinbe e Bege\N falharam na tentativa de assassinar Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E que o Luffy era o mentor do plano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Mentor do plano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, um pôster de procurados!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:21.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Minha recompensa subiu\N para 330 milhões de berries!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não acredito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:23.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Qual é a recompensa daquele musgo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Acho que a do Zoro-san é...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...320 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Toma essa, seu maldito musgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por causa de alguns números...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:40.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Voltaram a colocar "vivo ou morto"\N em vez de "apenas vivo"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Meu nome...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Agora diz Vinsmoke Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:59.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Minha recompensa aumentou\N por causa da fama da Germa!
