Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}S-Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Parece que tem alguém\N ainda mais deprimido lá!
