Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.68,0:05:10.43,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.68,0:05:10.43,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:06.68,0:05:10.43,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(960,52.5,960,-160,2500,3000)}Muito deprimido.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.08,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}Enquanto isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:23.54,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}Todos estão falando sobre o Reverie, a reunião dos líderes mundiais...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:30.13,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,981)}...que acontece na Terra Santa de Mary Geoise a cada quatro anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:34.64,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}E nós estamos na Ilha dos Homens-Peixe, a dez mil metros abaixo do nível do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.60,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}No Reino Ryugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eles conseguiram-yamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:43.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Jinbe finalmente se juntou\N à tripulação do Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:49.53,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.8\fs36.\fscx170\fscy170\fad(528,0)\pos(953,722)}REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:49.53,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.8\fs38\fscx170\fscy170\fad(528,0)\pos(958,1065)}REI NEPTUNE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:49.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Mas quem diria que os dois se uniriam\N para enfrentar a Big Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:06:00.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{=1}{\bord2.8\alpha&HF2&\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\move(520,780,1480,780,16,10426)}RYUBOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:06:00.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{=1}{\bord2.8\alpha&H00&\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\move(520,780,1480,780,16,10426)\fad(500,0)}RYUBOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:58.29,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{=0}{\bord2.8\alpha&HF2&\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\move(1265,780,2205,780,16,10426)}MANBOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:58.29,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{=0}{\bord2.8\alpha&H00&\bord2\fscx170\fscy171.32\move(1265,780,2205,780,16,10426)\fad(500,0)}MANBOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:06:00.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{=2}{\bord2.8\alpha&HEF&\bord2\fscx170\fscy170\move(90,770,496,780,12,4416)}FUKABOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:06:00.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{=2}{\bord2.8\alpha&H00&\bord2\fscx170.29\fscy170\move(90,770,496,780,12,4416)\fad(500,0)}FUKABOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:52.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Será que fugiram no mesmo navio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Jinbe e Chapéu de Palha-fa-so-la-si-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:06:00.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}O artigo diz que a Big Mom\N ficou furiosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:07.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Então este país terá que ser\N protegido pelos Chapéus de Palha-yamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:17.89,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.9\fs37.5\fscx170\fscy170\fad(487,0)\pos(960,721)}PRINCESA SHIRAHOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Eu também vou para o Reverie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:22.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Senão o Luffy-sama vai\N me chamar de Fracahoshi de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estava esperando que você dissesse isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Muito bem, vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:41.75,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}Porém, em vez de falar sobre a reunião que ainda nem começou, todos estão animados...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:46.13,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}...com a notícia de que Chapéu\N de Palha Luffy, o jovem pirata,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.21,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}desafiou Big Mom, a Yonkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:51.31,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}que durante décadas teve\N uma posição inabalável.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.30,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}O artigo diz o seguinte:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:58.01,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}"De acordo com uma de nossas fontes,\N Chapéu de Palha Luffy já é o líder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:01.56,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}...de sete poderosas tripulações piratas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:06.81,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}...com mais de cinco mil subordinados,\N tornando-o um grande capitão".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:11.28,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}"Também dizem que ele não foi\N apenas irmão de criação do Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.86,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,723)}mas também do Sabo, o segundo em\N comando do Exército Revolucionário".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:17.53,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}"Em um instante, ele conseguiu que\N a Germa 66, o exército maligno,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:22.33,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}os Piratas do Sol e os Piratas\N Fire Tank o obedecessem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.46,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}{\fad(0,513)}...devido ao seu carisma incomum\N e liderança".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:31.38,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}{\fad(0,514)}"Ele tem uma mente calculista, com a qual elaborou um plano que levou à destruição do castelo da rainha".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:37.01,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}"E tem a força para derrotar oficiais com\N recompensas de oitocentos milhões e um bilhão".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:41.81,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}"Não seria exagero considerar que\N o vencedor desta batalha foi Chapéu de Palha Luffy".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:45.02,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}Por fim, o artigo conclui dizendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:49.36,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}"É a ascensão do quinto\N Yonkou dos mares!".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Como assim quinto Yonkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Eu não ligo se esses piratas malignos...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:02.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}...ficam animados dizendo que\N há quatro ou cinco Yonkous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:02.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.2\fs37\fscx170\fscy170\fad(506,0)\pos(955,625)}QUARTEL GENERAL DA MARINHA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:02.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,300,,{\bord3.2\fscx170\fscy170\fad(506,0)\pos(960,1070)}SAKAZUKI - ALMIRANTE DA FROTA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Trago um relatório, Almirante da Frota Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:11.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O navio do Reino de Lulusia\N que está indo para o Reverie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...foi atacado por piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:18.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O rei está a salvo, mas\N sequestraram a princesa Comane...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Para que foram enviados então?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:26.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Xeque.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vovô!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que foi, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:40.76,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(199.5,97.5,199.5,-85.5,2290,2790)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.54,0:08:40.76,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(90,103.5,90,-79.5,2290,2790)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.54,0:08:40.76,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,2290,2790)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.54,0:08:40.76,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,2290,2790)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:35.54,0:08:40.76,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(960,52.5,960,-160,2290,2790)}Eles estão tentando assassinar Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}Você leu sobre o Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:41.34,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5\fs37.5\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)\fad(527,0)}REBECCA - ASSISTENTE REAL DE DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Sim, eu li. {tive que diminuir essas linhas por causa da nota necessária, mas como tem espaço, acho que ficou bom}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}Entendi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:43.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Luffyland é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não esperava menos do nosso chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:50.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}O jornal também menciona a gente...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:51.39,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.8\fs38\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)\fad(527,0)}LÍDER TONTA - TRIBO TONTATTA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:51.39,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.8\fs38\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,1070)\fad(527,0)}LEO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:56.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Pessoal, não falem sobre isso na Terra Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:01.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nós devemos muito a ele,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}mas o Governo Mundial e a Marinha o veem com outros olhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Exatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ele é um pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:13.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E não só isso, agora ele também será considerado um homem muito perigoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ele é impressionante...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vou mostrar isso para a Viola-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos mostrar para ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não há dúvida...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:28.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Esses são os navios de Dressrosa e do Reino Prodence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não há guardas da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E-Eu vejo a Princesa Viola!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ela é tão linda quanto dizem os rumores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}A garota com ela também é da família real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Se as sequestrarmos,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:43.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}quanto será que vão nos pagar de resgate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não é, Princesa Comane?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:49.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Liguem para o meu pai imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ele vai pagar todo o dinheiro que pedirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:56.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por isso que eu gosto de famílias reais!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Mas espere um pouco mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Somos muito gananciosos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:04.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eles nunca vão perceber que estamos aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:07.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...porque estamos escondidos nas profundezas do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Afundem eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:09.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Às ordens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:15.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É impossível se proteger de um ataque com torpedos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É um ataque inimigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Preparem os canhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:44.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:45.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não se preocupem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:52.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ainda bem que cheguei a tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vocês estão a salvo agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}V-Você é da Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.23,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(199.5,97.5,199.5,-85.5,1120,1620)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.23,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(90,103.5,90,-79.5,1120,1620)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.23,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,1120,1620)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.23,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,1120,1620)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.23,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(960,52.5,960,-160,1120,1620)}Justiça.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:11:00.56,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.8\fs37\fscx170\fscy170\fad(527,0)\pos(415,720)}CAPITÃO DO QUARTEL \NGENERAL DA MARINHA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:11:00.56,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs37\fscx170\fscy170\fad(527,0)\pos(417,1064)}KOBY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:11:00.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Eu sou Koby, um capitão do Quartel General da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nós falhamos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:04.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Isso não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estamos afundando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Tem algum ferido?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:17.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vocês são o comboio de Dressrosa e de Prodence, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Obrigado por aguentarem uma viagem tão longa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que acabou de acontecer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}De onde você surgiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu vim de um navio distante da Marinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:36.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Uns piratas atacaram este navio das profundezas do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nas profundezas do mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Com torpedos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ainda bem que erraram...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Helmeppo-san, como está indo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.86,Denden,,0,0,0,,{}Capturamos os piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:54.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.74,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs37.6\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,1066)\fad(527,480)}HELMEPPO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.74,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs37.6\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)\fad(527,480)}PRIMEIRO TENENTE DO QUARTEL GENERAL DA MARINHA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:57.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}A princesa Comane de Lulusia está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:58.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Malditos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:11:59.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Malditos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Espetem eles e assem-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Nunca vou perdoá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Claro, eles receberão a punição mais severa, princesa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:10.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}De qualquer forma, e o seu Kenbunshoku Haki, Koby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu não senti nenhum torpedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um submarino...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:20.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você não pode baixar a guarda com os piratas modernos...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quem diria...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você é o famoso Capitão Koby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:28.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O do incidente em Rocky Port?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:37.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Aquele incidente envolveu Trafalgar Law, que faz parte da Pior Geração...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:40.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Então você é o herói que protegeu os cidadãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E-Eu não sou herói nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:48.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu me perguntava como seria alguém tão corajoso, e vejo que você é um bom rapaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:51.30,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{}Esse homem é muito forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:55.51,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{}Nos salvou do ataque de um torpedo e não pede nem agradecimento...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:58.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}N-Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:12:59.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Digo, é Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ele chamou minha atenção \Nna matéria de capa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quer ler, Koby-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:07.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não, não.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:10.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Bem, então, vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:17.20,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{}O quinto imperador do mar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.58,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{}Luffy-san é incrível como sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:25.25,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{}Ele não para de avançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Koby-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.51,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{}Toda vez que te vejo no jornal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.76,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{}eu lembro daquele dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, Capitão Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que está fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Volte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Bem, em breve \Nchegaremos a Nova Marineford,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:02.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}então seremos sua escolta a partir de agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:04.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Contamos com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você gosta do Lucy, Koby-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:13.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você gosta do Luffyland, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:14.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}N-Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E-Ele é nosso inimigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não acredito em você...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos guardar segredo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos conversar um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Me solta, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}S-Sou da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Mas você parecia tão feliz \Nquando lia o jornal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}I-Isso foi porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos conversar, conversar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Pare, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Oh, o Luffyland também \Nsaiu nessa notícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, sabia que você gostava!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Minha recompensa aumentou, mas como foi por causa do sobrenome dos Germa,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:55.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}não estou nem um pouco feliz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:03.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Está com dor dos ferimentos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}N-Não é isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:07.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:12.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Minha recompensa diminuiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Olhem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É de cento e cinquenta milhões de berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:18.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:18.03,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sério mesmo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não tinha aumentado para \Nquinhentos milhões recentemente?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:27.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cento e cinquenta milhões é até menor \Ndo que a recompensa que você tinha há dois anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Como isso é possível?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você fez algo errado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nesse caso, aumentaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que importa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quanto menor, menos nos perseguirão.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:44.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nami-san, Luffy é nosso capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Pense no nosso prestígio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:47.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.90,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(522,0)\bord3\fs37.6\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)}GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.90,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(522,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\fs38\pos(960,1070)}UMA CIDADE PORTUÁRIA DO REINO DE LULUSIA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Atirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:05.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Roubem tudo que tiver de valor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E a Marinha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não vieram nos salvar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Como se atrevem a \Ndestruir nosso navio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que se dane a Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:29.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Seu rei foi para o Reverie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:33.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E levou suas melhores tropas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:38.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um país sem defesas é \Nalvo fácil para piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Escutem com atenção!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Sou um dos aliados \Ndo Yonkou Barba Negra,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:50.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}a quem foi concedido o \Nnome de Barba Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:52.58,OPLetreros,,0,0,270,,{\fad(529,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\fs37.5\pos(960,666)}CAPITÃO DOS PIRATAS \NBARBA ROSA - BARBA ROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:52.58,OPLetreros,,0,0,270,,{\fad(529,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,1070)}RECOMPENSA: 52 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Lembrem bem do meu nome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{}Temam o Barba Negra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:03.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Muito bem, homens, levem \Ntudo em nome de Barba Negra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Me dê seu dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:13.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}P-Pare, por favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não adianta se esconder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos queimar a cidade toda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, aguenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:24.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Fujam, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:34.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, não deixem essa garota escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Espere, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que você está escondendo aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:47.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Me entregue isso que você \Nestá segurando com tanto cuidado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:49.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Leite?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não é dinheiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:56.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Bem, vou levar mesmo assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É para as crianças da vila...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:10.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que ridículo defender \Nisso com tanta teimosia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por favor, me devolve...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:19.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Esse leite é muito importante.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estou te dizendo para \Nentregar seu dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não tenho dinheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:28.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você tem o que vai dar como \Ntributo celestial, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:34.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O-O tributo celestial é o que pagamos \Naos nossos governantes, ao rei e aos Tenryuubito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:39.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vivemos com austeridade \Ne economizamos todos os dias...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:43.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Se eu não pagar o tributo \Ncelestial, serei morta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que rei tirano.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, rapazes, procurem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:55.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estão escondendo o tributo celestial!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eles têm dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Peguem tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.50,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:02.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Me diga onde está o tributo celestial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Deixe-nos em paz...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Esta vila é pobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}P-Por favor, não levem esse dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Solte isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Socorro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:16.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não se machucariam \Nse apenas entregassem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Matem todos que desobedecerem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu te imploro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por favor, nos deixem em paz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos, Morley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E esse tremor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:52.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Tem algo debaixo da terra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um tridente gigante?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um gigante?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um, dois! Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:17.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:28.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um gigante saiu do chão!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E ainda por cima se veste \Nde um jeito esquisitíssimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por que ele está usando uma minissaia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Caramba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que estão olhando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:46.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por que estão me olhando assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:49.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Gostam tanto de mim assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você está realmente me acusando disso?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Qual é a história desse velho sujo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Seja como for, atirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:57.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Matem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:58.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não façam isso, jovens!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:09.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}G-Gigantes vivem debaixo da terra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nunca tinha visto um antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quem é ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não sejam maus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Parece que o chão virou argila!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não hesitem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:24.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Deve ser um usuário de Akuma no Mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:26.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Incrível...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:27.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E então?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que querem fazer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:32.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}escória...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:34.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...passiva?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:35.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:36.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Escória?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:38.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que devemos fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Com licença!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:41.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:43.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quem são vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:54.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Caramba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:58.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, ei, espera aí, Morley!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que você quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:08.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu inventei uma arma nova, \Nmas você se adiantou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:11.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quem são esses caras?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:18.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Um bando de corvos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:20.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:23.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}T-Tem uma pessoa \Nnaquele telhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:27.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Os corvos estão se reunindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:40.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Como se atrevem a machucar \Ngente indefesa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:43.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Capitão Barba Rosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:45.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Esses quatro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:49.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...supostamente estavam \Nespalhados pelo mundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:51.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}São os comandantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:53.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...do Exército Revolucionário!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:56.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O-Quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:03.91,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(398,0)\fs58.6\bord3.4\c&H000000&\3c&HD4E5DB&\xshad-6\yshad6\pos(1388,608)\fnPink Bunny 2}COMANDANTE DO BATALHAO OCIDENTAL \NDO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONARIO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Ei, parem de me encarar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:08.17,OPLetreros,,0,510,300,,{\fad(403,0)\fs58.6\bord3.4\c&H000000&\3c&HE8E6F0&\xshad-6\yshad6\fnPink Bunny 2\pos(562,608)}COMANDANTE DO BATALHAO ORIENTAL \NDO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONARIO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:08.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Não façam tanto barulho, escória!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:12.50,OPLetreros,,570,0,300,,{\fad(400,0)\fs58.6\bord3.4\c&H000000&\3c&HD0E5EC&\xshad-6\yshad6\fnPink Bunny 2\pos(1372,608)}COMANDANTE DO BATALHAO SUL \NDO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONARIO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Me deixem usar minha nova arma!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:17.01,OPLetreros,,0,580,300,,{\fad(405,0)\fs58.6\bord3.4\c&H000000&\3c&HF9EAF0&\xshad-6\yshad6\fnPink Bunny 2\pos(506,608)}COMANDANTE DO BATALHAO NORTE \NDO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONARIO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Não vamos deixar vocês fazerem o que quiserem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:20.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Os comandantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:22.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...do Exército Revolucionário...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:34.28,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(398,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,1070)}EMPORIO IVANKOV
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:34.28,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(398,0)\fscx170\fscy170\fs37.5\bord3\pos(960,720)}OFICIAL DO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:33.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Chapéu de Palha-boy é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:37.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Como era de esperar do seu filho.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:38.07,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(404,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,1070)}MONKEY D. DRAGON
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:38.07,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(404,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,720)}LÍDER DO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:38.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Além disso...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:42.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...não sabia que Sanji-boy era\N príncipe do Germa 66.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:46.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ele nunca mencionou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:47.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que insolente!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:52.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O Germa foi expulso do Governo \NMundial por causa desse incidente.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:54.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Chapéu de Palha-boy e Sanji-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.96,0:23:57.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Exatamente como eu esperava,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:24:01.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}estão no olho do furacão \Ndesta Grande Era da Pirataria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:24:01.51,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(404,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,1070)}INAZUMA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:24:01.51,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(404,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,720)}OFICIAL DO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:05.31,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(404,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,1070)}HACK
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:05.31,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(404,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,720)}SOLDADO DO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.51,0:24:03.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Os Chapéus de Palha...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:05.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}...me deixam tão emocionado.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:09.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}De qualquer forma, os oficiais estão atrasados.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:12.19,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(523,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,720)}INSTRUTORA ASSISTENTE DE KARATE \NHOMENS-PEIXE DO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:12.19,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(523,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,1070)}KOALA
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:12.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Eles já deveriam estar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:14.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você tem razão...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:18.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}A propósito, Sabo, o que você tem feito?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:23.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você não parou de olhar e sorrir \Npara o artigo sobre Luffy-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:25.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...até ficar com cãibra no rosto, não foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.66,0:24:27.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você é idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.37,0:24:31.63,Denden,,0,0,0,,{}Lindbergh falando!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:32.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que houve?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:34.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Estamos te esperando.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.13,0:24:35.30,Denden,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, é você Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:37.05,Denden,,0,0,0,,{}Estamos perto,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:39.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}mas temos um problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.09,0:24:40.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Se importam se atrasarmos \Num pouco?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sem problemas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:44.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Contanto que estejam bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.96,0:24:47.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, estou tão animado...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.31,0:24:51.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Todos os altos oficiais do \NExército Revolucionário vão se reunir aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.23,0:24:53.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vou poder ver Morley-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.98,0:24:56.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu amo Betty-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.98,0:24:59.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sabo, tempo é dinheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.95,0:25:01.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos nos reunir agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.24,0:25:04.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos aprimorar nosso plano \Nenquanto os esperamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.74,0:25:07.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É sua vez, chefe de gabinete.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.70,0:25:08.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.66,0:25:13.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}No próximo Reverie, finalmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.04,0:25:18.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Vamos declarar guerra, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.20,0:25:20.72,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{}{\fad(527,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,720)}CHEFE DE GABINETE DO \NEXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.20,0:25:20.72,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{}{\fad(527,0)\fscx170\fscy170\bord3\pos(960,1070)}SABO
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:20.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Contra os Tenryuubito.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.30,0:25:23.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Então, eles...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.84,0:25:25.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...são os comandantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.47,0:25:28.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...do Exército Revolucionário.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.02,0:25:33.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por que quatro oficiais \Ndeles estão aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.69,0:25:36.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Os jovens são tão violentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.56,0:25:39.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É porque eles gostam de você, seu gigante idiota.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.40,0:25:40.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não pode ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.24,0:25:41.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que nojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.19,0:25:43.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Já falei com Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.70,0:25:45.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos nessa, Betty?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.12,0:25:47.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ninguém pode nos deter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.49,0:25:51.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ninguém respondeu minha pergunta,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.04,0:25:53.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}e o que esse cara tá murmurando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.75,0:25:56.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não vou perdoar vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.38,0:25:58.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por que ele está tão irritado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.46,0:26:02.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que vão fazer, escória?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.34,0:26:04.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vão morrer ou lutar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.43,0:26:09.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Escolham seu próprio destino!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.81,0:26:14.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Acha que só os outros \Npodem ser heróis?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.06,0:26:21.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vocês também podem!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.05,0:26:44.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Os habitantes pegaram paus!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.17,0:26:45.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, ei, não me façam rir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.80,0:26:48.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Querem lutar contra a gente?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.31,0:26:54.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Por alguma razão me sinto inspirado \Ne mais forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.31,0:26:56.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos expulsar esses piratas daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.52,0:26:59.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos lutar para proteger nosso país!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.36,0:27:03.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.36,0:27:06.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Esse é o poder da Kobu Kobu no Mi da Betty!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.36,0:27:06.99,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(199.5,97.5,199.5,-85.5,3200,3630)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:27:03.36,0:27:06.99,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(90,103.5,90,-79.5,3200,3630)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:27:03.36,0:27:06.99,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,3200,3630)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:27:03.36,0:27:06.99,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,3200,3630)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:27:03.36,0:27:06.99,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(960,52.5,960,-160,3200,3630)}Animar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.99,0:27:11.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ao hastear sua bandeira, ela libera \No poder que dorme dentro das pessoas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.24,0:27:14.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Betty é a porta-bandeira da liberdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.75,0:27:17.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Agora, avancem!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.55,0:27:25.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Parece que não sabem a dor de um tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.63,0:27:27.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não sejam insolentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.89,0:27:31.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Lind, Karasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.68,0:27:32.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cubram eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.64,0:27:34.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Podem contar conosco!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.35,0:27:35.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Tomem isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.68,0:27:38.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cool Shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.68,0:27:38.56,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(199.5,97.5,199.5,-85.5,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:27:35.68,0:27:38.56,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(90,103.5,90,-79.5,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:27:35.68,0:27:38.56,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:27:35.68,0:27:38.56,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\fad(300,0)\move(87,108,87,-75,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:27:35.68,0:27:38.56,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1918,1078)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(960,52.5,960,-160,2500,3000)}Pistola de gelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.56,0:27:39.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Está gelado!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.81,0:27:41.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Minha arma congelou!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.61,0:27:42.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.69,0:27:45.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sumam daqui, piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.82,0:27:48.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não hesitem!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.11,0:27:50.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Exterminem eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.16,0:27:51.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Tirem as armas deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.92,0:27:59.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Os corvos levaram nossas espadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.67,0:28:00.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Devolvam elas!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.79,0:28:02.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não parem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.71,0:28:07.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Lutem contra seu destino!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.09,0:28:09.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sumam daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.22,0:28:17.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que aconteceu com todos de repente?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.10,0:28:19.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Maldito...!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:20.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Me devolva...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.31,0:28:25.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...o leite!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.30,0:28:46.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.50,0:28:49.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vocês vão pagar por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.17,0:28:51.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Barba Rosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.30,0:28:53.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sua recompensa é de 52 milhões, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.76,0:28:58.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Barba Negra-sama não vai\N ficar de braços cruzados...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.22,0:29:02.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Infelizmente ele não\N liga para seus subordinados.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.10,0:29:05.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, jovem!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.06,0:29:06.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.33,0:29:12.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ouçam, gente ignorante,\N covarde e fracote!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.03,0:29:19.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Se entregarem ele ao Governo Mundial,\Nvão ganhar a recompensa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.66,0:29:24.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}São 52 milhões de berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.04,0:29:25.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}E são...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:27.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...todos seus.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.67,0:29:32.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quero que levem isso também.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.34,0:29:36.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Para contatar o Exército Revolucionário.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.18,0:29:42.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Bom trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.31,0:29:43.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.65,0:29:46.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Podem nos chamar quando quiserem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.69,0:29:52.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Nunca abandonaremos os fracos\N que enfrentam as adversidades.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.58,0:30:06.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}B-Belo Betty-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.38,0:30:15.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Muito obrigada, membros\N do Exército Revolucionário!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.56,0:30:28.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ei, por que nos reunimos dessa vez?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.61,0:30:31.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Porque vamos desafiar os Tenryuubito.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.53,0:30:33.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, isso é ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.78,0:30:35.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Que emocionante!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.24,0:30:36.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ah, por sinal, Karasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.53,0:30:39.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Ligue seu alto-falante.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.95,0:30:44.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Esqueci...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.62,0:30:49.46,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}Faltam dois dias para o Reverie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.46,0:30:54.47,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}Os planos das pessoas do mundo todo\N começaram a girar em espiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.55,0:30:57.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Certo, entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.26,0:31:00.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Acabaram de nos chamar, Sabo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.31,0:31:03.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eles chegam logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.14,0:31:04.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Tudo bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.81,0:31:07.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.77,0:31:13.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que significa isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.15,0:31:19.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}Por que o idiota que arruinou\N meu negócio das Smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.63,0:31:22.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)\fad(527,0)}YONKOU
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.63,0:31:22.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,1070)\fad(527,0)}KAIDOU, O REI DAS FERAS
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.57,0:31:22.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\an8}...estava com essa velha?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.25,0:31:33.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}O que?! Ele nos venceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:36.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quando e contra quem eu perdi?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.26,0:31:39.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Foi ele, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.93,0:31:41.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Essa notícia deve ser coisa de...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.26,0:31:42.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.60,0:31:44.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você vai pagar por isso, Morgans...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.72,0:31:45.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.60,0:31:52.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Você vai pagar por isso,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.11,0:31:55.28,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,1070)\fad(426,0)\clip()}CHARLOTTE LINLIN
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.11,0:31:55.28,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)\fad(426,0)}BIG MOM, A YONKOU
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.61,0:31:55.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.32,0:31:59.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Imperador?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.87,0:32:01.91,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,1070)\fad(517,0)}MARSHALL D. TEACH
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.87,0:32:01.91,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)\fad(517,0)}BARBA NEGRA, O YONKOU
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.16,0:32:01.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{}{\an8}Ainda é cedo demais para você...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.88,0:32:12.67,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,1070)\fad(298,0)}SHANKS, O RUIVO
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.88,0:32:12.67,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord3\fscx170\fscy170\pos(960,720)\fad(298,0)}YONKOU
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.67,0:32:14.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Parece...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.30,0:32:15.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...que nos veremos em breve,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.80,0:32:19.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.14,0:32:31.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Bom, se diminuiu, não há\N nada que possamos fazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.35,0:32:33.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Anime-se, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.56,0:32:35.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Eu vou te ajudar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.19,0:32:36.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vamos continuar nos esforçando.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.58,0:32:39.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Quer que eu prepare algo para comer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.66,0:32:41.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:49.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Esperem um momento, por favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.63,0:32:55.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Vejam...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.84,0:33:00.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cem mil, um milhão, dez milhões...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.05,0:33:02.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}Cem milhões...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.89,0:33:07.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}S-Sua recompensa...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.35,0:33:13.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}...é de um bilhão e quinhentos milhões de berries!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.94,0:33:19.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{}{\fad(0,555)}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.94,0:33:19.11,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,{}{\fad(0,555)}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.99,0:33:23.11,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}O mundo inteiro se dirige\N ao Reverie e, por outro lado,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.11,0:33:25.87,Principio,,0,0,0,,{}os Chapéus de Palha estão\N a caminho do País de Wano.
